comments: Nurkic (PHX) jumps alongside Williams Jr. (MEM) and marginal body contact occurs during Williams Jr.'s (MEM) outward arm as he shields himself during the shot attempt.
Williams (MEM) brings his right hand forward and makes contact with the ball when Allen (PHX) pursues the defensive rebound.
Nurkic (PHX) firms over to his left shoulder in Williams' (MEM) path and absorbs the contact to set the pick.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) jumps vertically and absorbs the contact initiated by Beal (PHX) during the driving shot attempt.
Nurkic (PHX) moves alongside Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Nurkic (PHX) establishes himself in Smart's (MEM) path and his legs remain within the frame of his body as contact occurs, which he does not deliver.
Williams (MEM) brings his right hand forward and cleanly blocks Nurkic's (PHX) shot attempt near the basket.
Williams Jr. (MEM) and Nurkic (PHX) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Smart (MEM) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Beal (PHX) prior to incidental arm contact occurring.
Allen (PHX) makes clean contact with the ball to dislodge it away from Williams (MEM) before incidental contact occurs with his arm during the layup attempt.
Allen (PHX) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds. The Grizzlies retain possession of the ball.
Allen (PHX) attempts to go for the steal and initiates body contact with Bane (MEM), affecting Bane's SQBR.

Replay review of the foul called on Jackson Jr. (MEM) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Jackson Jr. (MEM) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact with Booker (PHX) which affects his driving shot attempt.
Smart (MEM) wraps and dislodges Booker (PHX) off-ball during the inbound.
Bates-Diop (PHX) commits a take foul on Bane (MEM).
